*********************************

Discription:
	Cpu Monitor is a little widget coded in python that makes
use of the pygame module for a neatly organized GUI that displays
critical CPU information.

Requirements:
sysstat installed
python 2.x installed
pygame installed
tkinter installed

Instructions:
	Install the required software on linux before trying to run cpu monitor.
Once that is complete, attempt to run the program from the commandline via
python cpu.py, and deal with any errors if they arise before attempting to run
the program again.

